p213
aS'When Social Security began making monthly distributions in 1940, there were 160 workers for every senior receiving benefits.'
p214
aS'Today, there are about three workers.'
p215
aS'And within two decades, there will be two.'
p216
aS'Demographic are destiny.'
p217
aS'The message could not be clearer.'
